@screensguru We are excited to announce the launch of the 11 all woman AI artists group exhibition [𝚃𝚁𝚄𝚂𝚃 𝚃𝙷𝙴 𝙱𝙻𝙾𝙾𝙼] curated by @elluba Luba Elliott, @lung_shuk Wai Lung Ip & @uyretep Peter Yu via a series of panels, exhibitions & guided tours online & offline starting at end of June to Sep at www.screensguru.io

The exhibitions aims to expand the imagination of Generative Art through artistic expressions and technologies.

Artists showcased in this exhibition come from two distinct backgrounds. Some are trained coder/ artists with a background in computer science, capable of writing and customizing the tools they use in their artistic expression. Yet others come with existing artistic practices, and choose to leverage AI and other computation tools to tell their stories.

Let’s celebrate the blooming of Generative Art.

Curatorial statement is advised by Sunny Tsoi, PhD in medical science, Karolinska Institute

